                <p class="paragraph_style_2">My research interest is in the field of Computer Vision and Machine Learning. The idea to have artificial machines able to solve high-level human tasks has always fascinated me and comes as a thrill, in particular when dealing with vision tasks. My work involves the design or adaptation of machine learning algorithms followed by experimental prototyping and testing. At the same time, by personal attitude, I like to see things working in practice, a reason for why I also enjoy developing software, creating final products easily accessible to other users/researchers.<br /></p>
